snippet: Russia’s glamorous political-opposition couple, Kseniya Sobchak and Ilya Yashin, are no more. Ms. Sobchak has surprised Moscow by marrying another man.
abstract: Unlikely romance between Russian socialite Kseniya Sobchak and political activist Ilya Yashin publicly ends when Sobchak announces on her Twitter account that she has married another man.
lead_paragraph: Russia’s glamorous political-opposition couple, Kseniya Sobchak and Ilya Yashin, are no more. Ms. Sobchak has surprised Moscow by marrying another man.

headline.seo: Kseniya Sobchak, Russian Celebrity, Marries, and the Groom Is Not Yashin
headline.main: Twitter End to Love Story Born in Russia’s Protests
